Juditachea pustokant eke ostorie vorvim desachi suttka zata, tech porim hea-I pustokant Esther ostorie udexim desachi suttka zata tem vornnilam.  Hamanak Ahasuerus razan unch zuttiek venchun kaddlolo.  To ekdom virodhi ani podvedar aslo.  Hamanak lagun Persient vosti korun aslolea Judevancho jiv sonkottant aslo.  Punn iogia velar ek tornnatti Judev ostori Esther ranni zali ani Mordekai hachem margdorxon gheun Judevank sonkottantle vattaile.  Hea somoiar sogllem bodolta.  Hamanak gollar choddoitat,  Mordekai tacho zago gheta, Judev aplea dusmanak jivexim marun uddoitat. Ani hem zoit somarombhunk Purim’ Utsov sthaptat ani dor vorsa to somarombhunk nem’ kortat. 

Adlea kallar lok Judevancho dves konn porim kortalo, tem hea Estherachea pustokant dakhoilam.  Judev lok kuxin ani eklim – eksurim jietalim, haka lagun her lok ani raza porian tancho dves kortale.  Antiokus Epifanesache piddapiddecho ugddas kor.  Hea pustokant khub rogot varovlolem polleun, amkam ‘dhok’ko bostolo’ pun hem pustok Kristi ap-porgottnne adim boroilolem mhonn ugddas dhorlear boro.  

Grik bhaxent, Estherachem pustok 114 (va 78) Kristi Xoka adim thaun aslem. Purim’cho utsov os’sol mhonn mhor  marunk hem pustok Ejiptak dhaddlolem.  ( Polle Est. 10/31).  Tea von adim Hebrev bhaxent Estherachem pustok aslem 160 Krista Xoka adim  ( Polle 2 Mak. 15/36),   Palestinantle Judev, “Mordekaiacho Dis” somarombhtale.  Hea vorvim Estherachem pustok aslem mhonn spoxtt zata.

